Package: mark-on-doubleclick
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Mark messages read on double-click in Evolution (EPlugin)
 A minimal Evolution plugin that leaves previewed messages Unread and marks
 them Read when opened in their own window (double-click). Owner-only UI.
